{"tid":2338378,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有人鼓吹平安夜參與未經批准集結 警方已部署足夠警力果斷執法","createTime":"2020-12-24T03:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T05:32:34.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b9a00f774f6027f732e5e396c361325523bf48","tid":2338378,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"【有人鼓吹平安夜參與未經批准集結 警方已部署足夠警力果斷執法】<br />\n【Netizens called for Unauthorized Assemblies on Christmas Eve   Adequate Police Deployment to Enforce the Law Resolutely】<br />\n<br />\n警方留意到有人於網上號召他人於今日（12月24日）在全港各區進行未經批准的集結。警方提醒公眾，有關活動並沒有獲得警方的不反對通知書，參與、組織或煽惑他人參與未經批准集結或非法集結，均有機會觸犯《公安條例》，一經定罪最高可被判處監禁5年 。<br />\n<br />\n此外，有關行為亦會增加病毒在社區傳播的風險及有可能違反《預防及控制疾病(禁止羣組聚集)規例》（第599G章）下有關進行受禁羣組聚集的規定。<br />\n<br />\n疫情仍然嚴峻，警方呼籲市民應遵守相關法例，做好防疫措施，並應盡量減少社交活動及避免到人多聚集的地方。警方絕不容忍任何違法行為，再次呼籲市民不要參與任何未經批准集結或受禁的羣組聚集。警方會在相關地點部署足夠警力，迅速果斷執法，維護法紀。<br />\n<br />\nThe Police are aware that some netizens incited others to take part in unauthorised assemblies in various districts across the territory today (24 December).  The Police would like to remind the public that no Letter of No Objection has ever been issued for the proposed public events.   Anyone who organises, participates in or incites others to participate in any unauthorised or unlawful assembly risks committing the offences under the Public Order Ordinance, and on conviction, shall be liable to a maximum penalty of five years' imprisonment.  <br />\n<br />\nBesides, participation in public gatherings will also increase the risk of transmission of the virus in the community and may commit certain offences under the Prevention and Control of Disease (Prohibition on Group Gathering) Regulation (Cap. 599G)  regarding prohibited group gatherings.<br />\n<br />\nThe Police call upon members of the public to refrain from taking part in unauthorised assemblies and prohibited group gatherings amid the COVID-19 pandemic. The Police do not condone any illegal and violent acts, and will take resolute action to enforce the law."},{"pid":"fb97b1f52ef5cbae0c7d24fb0137d14407e85a65","tid":2338378,"uid":50386,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"慶祝平安夜係咪要申請不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a748c945a266f5fd3016dead5baa9f5edcd9535","tid":2338378,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:42:34.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎攬炒曬香港經濟"},{"pid":"e685da809a361d8e65c6d50a426c68b48b82c29d","tid":2338378,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"連自編都懶， 直接作故仔"},{"pid":"4ad228a051984ea96943f23f9ff8936e1f2cc29b","tid":2338378,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:43:46.000Z","msg":"乜果斷 正一垃圾"},{"pid":"8683030a4d09d96fdf9b3996c4355db1022392c3","tid":2338378,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:45:11.000Z","msg":"Joey英文好差"},{"pid":"b17201f8f4f325e347b7b0c26b1279126b172da2","tid":2338378,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wYUNwX1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwYUNwX1.jpg&h=e09da15d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37218158e62019fba00e8cbb47e6d31ab9c3da58","tid":2338378,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"大家千萬唔好叫人出街<br />\n各大商戶唔好亂咁宣傳<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母個政府真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c33ad8137d3c4d4999f4a927c24cc8377c80b35","tid":2338378,"uid":325580,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:56:41.000Z","msg":"可能大家睇唔明狗文我翻譯下：<br />\n可能已經確診嘅黑警將在香港各區組織非法聚集，唔想染武漢肺炎stay home plz<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/do